OL,5, The son of a woman abused by a double  
OL,6, killer in a hospital morgue has said he
OL,7, is channelling his anger by fundraising
OL,8, in his mother's memory.                
OL,10,FDavid Fuller, 67, of East Sussex,      
OL,11,Fabused at least 100 women and girls in 
OL,12,Ftwo Kent morgues over 12 years.        
OL,14,FIn October, the family of Tania        
OL,15,FMackelden from Staplehurst, who died in
OL,16,F2017, were told she was a victim.      
OL,18,FHer son, Tom Mackelden, said: "You lose
OL,19,Fthem once and then you feel like you   
OL,20,Flose them all over again."             
